      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAPPY TOO YA (1) faces a stiffer test tonight but he is flying having put four wins together. Led in each of those so has the gate speed to take full advantage of the inside draw. REWATCH (10) is a handy colt who has joined Luke McCarthy since a second here three weeks ago. Has only once missed the top-two in his last five outings and is good enough to win with even luck from a wide draw. LAYDEN (7) is a player after a solid fourth from a similar barrier here last time. MONTEFIORE NZ (2) resumes off some decent form including a win at this circuit and distance two back. Readied with a trial and is aided by a good draw. RIVERA LOU (5) chased an in-form rival to place last start and came from this barrier when he scored four back at this circuit and distance.",
